HEADWORD: Thurification
<hw>Thu`ri*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>thus</ets> incense + <ets>-ficare</ets> (in comp.) to make. See
<er>-fy</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of fuming with incense, or the act of
burning incense.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thuringian</ent>⟦br⟧
